(define/contract (incremovable-subarray-count nums)
  (-> (listof exact-integer?) exact-integer?)
  
  (define (is-strictly-increasing? lst)
    (or (null? lst)
        (null? (cdr lst))
        (and (< (car lst) (cadr lst))
             (is-strictly-increasing? (cdr lst)))))

  (define (remove-subarray lst start end)
    (append (take lst start) (drop lst (+ 1 end))))

  (define (count-incremovable-subarrays lst)
    (let ([n (length lst)])
      (define (iter start end count)
        (cond
          [(>= start n) count]
          [(>= end n) (iter (+ start 1) (+ start 1) count)]
          [else
           (let ([new-lst (remove-subarray lst start end)])
             (iter start (+ end 1)
                   (if (is-strictly-increasing? new-lst)
                       (+ count 1)
                       count)))]))
      (iter 0 0 0)))

  (count-incremovable-subarrays nums))
